name: Post war-war
description: Cupid is dealing with multiple personalities. In one life he is a little child that accepts that this conflict will never end. In another he believes that he should grow up and get involved in this never-ending war. At night a voice whispers to him “I can’t take it anymore” / Cube – A solved puzzle that doesn’t stop spinning for the solution is available but nobody wants to acknowledge./ Eggplant – It represents a burning Middle East. For thousands of years this region remained a battleground for the illusive powers.
